multiplicity3.csys.items.line

Interface ILine

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IItem, INestable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ICachableLine
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CachableLine, JMELine

    public interface ILine
extends IItem
    This line will link two items together such that when those items are updated, the line will be updated too.
    Author:
    dcs0ah1
